author: Unreal Engine
description:
It's Unreal Fest week in Stockholm and on Tuesday we'll be joined by SoWhen? CEO Mohamed Marouene as he takes us through how they helped Flexis embrace Unreal Engine.

Flexis' goal is to revolutionize urban logistics for package delivery. Cutting-edge technology meets the last mile of logistics in this talk that really delivers!: http://epic.gm/unreal-fest-stockholm-agenda
title: Unreal Fest Stockholm Meet the Presenter: Mohamed
